## Success Criteria

The implementation is complete when:

1. ✅ **System boots to Orbit**: After installation and reboot, user sees Orbit UI, not Windows Explorer
2. ✅ **Applications work normally**: User can launch and use any Windows application
3. ✅ **Window management works**: Can move, resize, minimize, maximize, close windows via custom decorations
4. ✅ **Input is correctly routed**: Clicking and typing in applications works normally
5. ✅ **Taskbar is functional**: Can see running apps, launch new apps
6. ✅ **System is stable**: Can run for hours without crashes or memory leaks
7. ✅ **Clean uninstall**: Can restore Windows to Explorer with no issues
8. ✅ **Safe mode works**: Can boot to Explorer if Orbit has problems

